title: Easy Crooning (feat. Dave Attell, Joe DeRosa & Ali Siddiq)
description: Jay thinks crooning is easy singing & Joe DeRosa is offended. Dave Attell let’s everyone know how his quarantine is going. Ali Siddiq gives an report on how his home state of Texas is opening up. EaJay and Dan explore the idea of doing fan cam website.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
